java.awt.datatransfer.Transferable
public class GUITransferable
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.awt.datatransfer.Transferable

This class implements the transferable functionalities for drag-and-drop. It represents the file being dragged from the file explorer to the OpenGL interface.
